0.1.name: wordpress/wistia-wordpress-oembed-plugin
0.1.description: Wistia's embed codes are designed to be very durable, but WordPress has a history of being particularly troublesome. This plugin transparently makes sure that your Wistia embeds will work, no matter what you do.
